      <section eId="sec_13_3_22">
        <num>13-3-22</num>
        <content>
          <p>Marriage contracts and settlements made by persons who are minors but of lawful age to marry are binding as if made by adults.</p>
          <p>(Orig. Code 1863, § 2696; Code 1868, § 2692; Code 1873, § 2734; Code 1882, § 2734; Civil Code 1895, § 3651; Civil Code 1910, § 4236; Code 1933, § 20-204.)</p>
